{"tid":1084241,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世文] 各位巴打 !! 一定要照顧好自己棚牙啊 !!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-03-30T09:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T19:38:13.000Z","uid":75100,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"157193f28cbb449f2d13138128f8c6935b82c180","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"本身自己都好耐無去牙醫度check，因為唔洗牙都算白，就掉而輕心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申返而家既狀況，有7-8處蛀牙，同埋本身一年前左右，第一小臼齒咬到硬野崩左，痛左一晚無事，就一直無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到早排同一個位又咬到，神經痛到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個陣隻牙已經接近無左40%左右<br />\n<br />\n大家如果咬崩左隻牙，一定一定要盡早去睇牙醫呀!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為一穿左洞，d細菌就仲易入去，本身蛀牙會變到仲嚴重，拖耐左，用既錢就會幾倍幾倍咁上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同大家講下，好似我呢個情況，無左大部份牙齒，就到神經線，可以點做? 無錯，就係杜牙根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過程好似下圖咁，簡單黎講，杜牙根= 殺死你隻牙入面既神經，變左死牙就唔會痛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMVNkmM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMVNkmM.gif&h=e5c02655&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n話說小弟琴日就去左杜，d姑娘都幾好笑容，個醫生都好pro咁，同我講解要分幾次做，一次開牙放藥，一次拔神經線.....etc，咁我撚識咩，咪係咁5555<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生話同我打麻醉藥，本身我想話唔撚使啦，我好忍得痛，之前睇骨科連屎眼都比人用力捅左成分鐘，但個醫生話第一次會好痛，咁我咪是但<br />\n<br />\n一開始打左藥，塊面都會有d感覺，慢慢開始麻，然後醫生開始鑽鑽鑽鑽鑽鑽鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中下程度既神經痛，仲接受到，係心理上淆底，我心諗: 濕濕碎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直至醫生攞左呢條野出黎.....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k56HTE5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk56HTE5.png&h=8fd80013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nhey, what up man? 這是什麼? 停手呀喂!!!<br />\n醫生係咁用呢枝野插入牙齒深處，勁用力咁上下磨擦，1枝仲唔夠，足足3-4枝!!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全身唔敢郁，個心臟feel到係咁跳，但其實唔算超痛........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後埋單，$4500+ 未來整牙冠= 1萬左右，真係請各位巴打多多注意牙齒健康，因為如果我一早去醫，完全唔使杜，可能用既錢都少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83931e13b265e9a02794fdeafa2fdfd5fbbb4743","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"總結<br />\n1) 定期去牙醫度，因為就算你d牙好白，無牙痛，好大機會腳根位都有蛀，肉眼係睇唔到的，初期有都好容易搞<br />\n<br />\n2) 一定要刷牙，唔好太大力，而家晚晚用緊漱口水，唔知有無用，反正做左先<br />\n<br />\n3) 甜同酸既野戒唔到架啦，盡量少吃吧<br />\n<br />\n4)咬崩左隻牙，一定要快d去睇牙醫，再唔理隨時要杜<br />\n<br />\n5)嚴重牙齒問題就唔好貪平，咪撚返大陸整牙!! 我自己都有考慮過，但來回咁耐，精神上會好累，同埋牙就一世既，你話淘寶食物/衣服，ok， 但大陸醫院整衰左你就一世，香港醫生整衰左你，你仲可以搵東張西望屌7佢"},{"pid":"6a9da8aa4bad9361afd347a37b4ef9b2693f8309","tid":1084241,"uid":26535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"之前都差少少要杜牙根 跟住照片話其實可以試下補(補到) 之後每年check一次牙洗一次牙 <br />\n<br />\nCheck牙一定照片唔用肉眼試 一張片150-200(2張)但可保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff069f0053276e81c0fe85db9a48bf2b6480748","tid":1084241,"uid":26535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"推 大家要照顧好佢"},{"pid":"c81ef8eccac3ce48983a76e8d34830f7f960d8f2","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9da8aa4bad9361afd347a37b4ef9b2693f8309","tid":1084241,"uid":26535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"之前都差少少要杜牙根 跟住照片話其實可以試下補(補到) 之後每年check一次牙洗一次牙 <br />\n<br />\nCheck牙一定照片唔用肉眼試 一張片150-200(2張)但可保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"巴打你真好彩，我杜之前其實都有補過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然外觀靚仔返，但事後入面d神經痛到爆炸，無辨法先杜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後生仔邊個想無左隻真牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽醫生講，而家基本杜完，個牙冠用2-30年都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704ec6f884b94dd2937c0d88b03d5f42d245eddc","tid":1084241,"uid":82332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />thx.搵日check下"},{"pid":"74c4bc9eab70265853ff15affd05ddbcc3fb73f8","tid":1084241,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"好多人根本唔識刷牙<br />\n淨係拉鋸刷,藏晒牙石<br />\n又成日夜晚唔刷牙<br />\n夜晚瞓左冇口水分泌阻止細菌滋生<br />\n朝早刷都補唔返"},{"pid":"996414f5f127f5d4b9bcd832796845acd647ff7c","tid":1084241,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"見到支嘢都牙軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea684336a95dc8392c1ba3715ec31bc174805690","tid":1084241,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"四隻大牙都杜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cb2819eac42e5be9375812952c8bf96f795fd9","tid":1084241,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9f2d2fc2768532a033fa2946c80be67a2772e731","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea684336a95dc8392c1ba3715ec31bc174805690","tid":1084241,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"四隻大牙都杜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"巴打唔計衫，已經帶左4萬蚊係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食野使唔使就力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a658a8d0e3aba793edd09d135dad27f9a639d873","tid":1084241,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f2d2fc2768532a033fa2946c80be67a2772e731","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea684336a95dc8392c1ba3715ec31bc174805690","tid":1084241,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"四隻大牙都杜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"巴打唔計衫，已經帶左4萬蚊係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食野使唔使就力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"我好似中學已經杜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔覺有咩事 牙醫話要框唔係會甩<br />\n我又冇框都好有力<br />\n平平安安過左十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a5bc6d9fa8204277b7703d8187198489a0dc07","tid":1084241,"uid":242184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:18:26.000Z","msg":"屯門有無邊個牙醫補牙 洗牙好介紹？"},{"pid":"ac65097071a0a3f566b98614120e8932866f1c1a","tid":1084241,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"有杜幾隻。<br />\n<br />\n唔好到牙痛先去睇牙醫，牙感覺到痛，蛀牙位已經到神經。其實蛀牙好易有，好早檢查到，好易補到就無咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">窮撚係大陸整</span>"},{"pid":"2097c6412b07231c9b1a0454dbe83636756db14a","tid":1084241,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"157193f28cbb449f2d13138128f8c6935b82c180","tid":1084241,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"本身自己都好耐無去牙醫度check，因為唔洗牙都算白，就掉而輕心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申返而家既狀況，有7-8